age.Description: Participant's age in years. n/a means there was no response from participant though a response was possible. Question may have been skipped over by participant.

Levels.n/a: No response, meaning there was no response from participant though a response was possible. Question may have been skipped over by participant.

handedness.Description: Handedness is decided based on Laterality Quotient ranges from the Edinburgh Handedness Inventory.  See Levels below for exact ranges.

Levels.n/a: No data available for a response.  The question was not presented or asked to the participant.
